  <h1>International Payment and Shipping Options</h1>
  <h2>Payment Options</h2>
  <ul>
  	<li>Cash in Advance by wire transfer (Please inquire about bank information)</li>
  	<li>Credit Card (Mastercard or Visa)</li>
  	<li>30 day Open Credit Terms (Prior authorization required)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Shipping Options</h2>
  <p>Sonnax will arrange shipment to you, your freight forwarder or your designated carrier.</p>
  <ul>
